      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "(And, how good is a good one?)",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "It’s hard to gauge what ‘good enough’ looks like unless you can discern between what’s acceptable and what isn’t.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "It’s easy when everything is really good (or really bad). But it gets trickier when it’s not so clear cut.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Having a checklist, and some firm rules, usually helps.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Saying: ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "these things",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " have to be done and if they aren’t it’s ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "not acceptable",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": ",” is a lot easier than saying, “do your best.”",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "It’s also way more efficient than relying on good judgement, only to find out later that your output isn’t meeting spec.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}